{"tid":1514353,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【有圖】烏溪沙站巴士站出口髮型鋪懷疑玩鳩年輕人","createTime":"2019-08-28T16:56:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T04:07:17.000Z","uid":57762,"like":6,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2b55c26cca7891e243968e8a505a52c9262816af","tid":1514353,"uid":57762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T16:56:42.000Z","msg":"一個金毛四眼阿叔剪嘅，洗剪188嗰間。<br />\n佢話剪完之後，我指住個角同佢講想再剪少少，唔想起角(金正恩咁樣)，講完之後佢都唔撚明，我就再講多次，條仆街態度都唔係幾好，串柒柒咁，串鳩我話邊到有角，我都係叫佢剪，點知個直角變撚咗做兩個角！<br />\n<br />\n我嬲嬲地即刻話得就俾錢走人，返到屋企自己剃咗兩隻角，唔記得剃前影相<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n隔一陣又發現右邊俾狗咬咁，而且好似特登剃光<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pnSBfmk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpnSBfmk.jpg&h=72515788&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n極懷疑條仆街一係垃圾，係廢閪唔識剪；一係就<span style=\"color: red;\">玩鳩年輕人</span>，幫你亂鳩咁剪。"},{"pid":"852075f8ed8e10edb7a1d73987f063f8e3bc6c0a","tid":1514353,"uid":124048,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T16:59:23.000Z","msg":"開名啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"899b024c6691f66c5e5224b20aa5b213ca839016","tid":1514353,"uid":57762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"852075f8ed8e10edb7a1d73987f063f8e3bc6c0a","tid":1514353,"uid":124048,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T16:59:23.000Z","msg":"開名啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T17:09:53.000Z","msg":"得一間<br />\nLa Palma(應該係)<br />\n電話：+852 2831 4388<br />\n地址：沙田馬鞍山銀湖天峰地下G11號舖<br />\n(上網揾)<br />\n<br />\n仲話係大公司，屌<br />\n個阿叔連相都冇係官網出現！得另外兩個人有相"},{"pid":"41223938345ad3071c20acf5f6880e27ca557d76","tid":1514353,"uid":57762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T17:12:12.000Z","msg":"佢班同事<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oXNYCMU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoXNYCMU.png&h=3cd4411b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4Dn9KrV.png\" 